Introduction

Im Do Hwa (formerly known as Chan Mi) is a South Korean singer, rapper, and actress under FNC Entertainment. She is the maknae of the girl group AOA and a member of its sub-unit AOA Cream.

In 2023, she participated in the Kakao Entertainment virtual reality survival show "GIRL'S RE:VERSE". Her final rank was #26.

Also in 2023, she participated in the Mnet survival show "Queendom Puzzle", but was eliminated at 14th place.
